comments.body:
In commit "mining: add submitBlock IPC method to Mining interface" (5b60f69e40ac1ec2b2f4276e2529914813cd22e5)

It would seem good to check assumptions this code is making to avoid bugs where reason is unset when this returns false, or set when this returns true. Maybe:

```
CHECK_NONFATAL(accepted && new_block == reason.empty());
return accepted && new_block;
```

